Class SegmentedParserError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.SegmentedParserError
  • public final class SegmentedParserError
extends Object
    Defines the possible errors that can be returned when creating a ISegmentedAsset from a manifest.

    ISegmentedAsset
